{"product_id":"grey-basic-bottoms","title":"GREY BASIC BOTTOMS","description":"\u003cp\u003e MODEL HEIGHT 5'10 AND WAIST SIZE 32 WEARING M BOTTOMS.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n420 GSM TAPED COTTON FLEECE\u003cbr\u003e\nCOMBED \u0026amp; BIO-WASHED FINISH\u003cbr\u003e\nSTRAIGHT BAGGY FIT\u003cbr\u003e\nMELANGE GREY MINIMAL DESIGN\u003cbr\u003e\nUNISEX ARTICLE [REFER TO SIZE CHART FOR ACCURATE MEASUREMENTS]. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCrafted from 420 GSM premium taped cotton fleece for a structured yet soft feel with long-lasting durability.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStraight baggy silhouette offers relaxed comfort and effortless everyday styling.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eClean, blank design allows versatile pairing with any outfit, from elevated basics to statement layers.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMelange grey tone adds depth and refinement while remaining easy to style year-round.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTaped fleece construction enhances structure while maintaining flexibility and comfort.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePerfect for all seasons, balancing warmth, breathability, and premium weight.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMachine wash the bottoms inside out with similar colors.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUse cold water to maintain fabric quality and color texture.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eTumble dry on low heat or air dry to preserve structure.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStore folded in a cool, dry place to retain shape and finish.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e420 GSM taped fleece construction for a substantial premium feel.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStraight baggy fit designed for comfort and versatile styling.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eUnisex silhouette suited for multiple body types.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBlank minimal design for effortless outfit pairing.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eElasticated waist for adjustable comfort and everyday wear.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eBalanced fabric weight ideal for all-season use.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":46885165072538,"sku":"Reign4","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"M","offer_id":46885165105306,"sku":"Reign4","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":46885165138074,"sku":"Reign4","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46885165170842,"sku":"Reign4","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":46885165203610,"sku":"Reign4","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":46885165236378,"sku":"Reign4","price":1899.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00452copy_11zon.jpg?v=1772290145","url":"https:\/\/dripdrip.in\/products\/grey-basic-bottoms","provider":"DRIP STUDIOS","version":"1.0","type":"link"}